表格上传记录流水表主表的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('DataHistoryMain')
and type = 'U')
drop table DataHistoryMain
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: DataHistoryMain */
/*==============================================================*/
create table DataHistoryMain (
ID int identity(1,1),
MachineNo varchar(20) not null,
MouldNo varchar(20) not null,
WorkOrderNo varchar(20) not null,
DispatchOrder varchar(20) not null,
ProductNo varchar(20) not null,
ClientIP varchar(20) null,
TotalNum int not null,
GoodNum int null,
BadNum int null,
MachineStatus int null,
MachineCycletime decimal(8,2) not null default (0),
CycleTime decimal(8,2) not null default (0),
BeginCycle datetime not null,
EndCycle datetime null,
CreateTime datetime not null,
constraint PK_DATAHISTORYMAIN primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
